{"tid":299043,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好嬲自己咁幼稚","createTime":"2017-06-26T17:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T00:52:27.000Z","uid":65256,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3682f7057008d287b9324c3e4cfc1f5d2ece2cf8","tid":299043,"uid":65256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"成日小小野就唔想出聲 唔想理人咁<br />\n例如熱得濟就唔想理人<br />\n眼瞓又唔想理人<br />\n唔舒服都會唔想理人<br />\n總之一心情差就控制唔到咁西口西面<br />\n明明唔想咁樣對人 但真係控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好鬼憎自己情緒管理咁差"},{"pid":"90f6c2fc124c06a77f76d4f0d9b084011aa89a38","tid":299043,"uid":94182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"好正常啫<br />\n肚餓得濟個人會燥<br />\n熱得濟我都會唔想講野同黑面<br />\n我ex勁鍾意係呢個時候摸我肚<br />\n屌鳩佢又嬲鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a409570b02f619c84489252c592ec325be7860","tid":299043,"uid":75707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:59:49.000Z","msg":"好正常姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有人會日日充滿能量"},{"pid":"45a53db5689d0afe6e644a474c165d9c4011d6a9","tid":299043,"uid":120581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:40:06.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"ebd9655238766459326207a5fb9550ccbe894055","tid":299043,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:52:30.000Z","msg":"係office 長期閪面個d就真係乞人憎喇"},{"pid":"2b75ed06f8b83227ac565d1c6e2cc8a7de997b1c","tid":299043,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"我都成日係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016e3cd2c46ded8f9d5f371deed062e5731a9241","tid":299043,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:26:34.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見人又慢手慢腳又蠢就忟 <br />\n天氣熱又忟<br />\n番屋企見部lift喺最高要等佢落嚟都會忟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點先可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f8535d11ba64dd24f050af768f9ce31494bde9","tid":299043,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:30:15.000Z","msg":"心情唔好  發洩下情緒好正常啫"},{"pid":"063f8486f94f9daeb803c69a6a7ffe0620f2c650","tid":299043,"uid":64512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T20:22:26.000Z","msg":"自問都算忍得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係一熱一焗個人就會勁炆勁燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上果陣邊個同我講野果個人就會變左出氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我諗咁樣好正常姐 應該好多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f2ea577983a1c0221d992bf9ec6c73fa8c5296","tid":299043,"uid":81751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T20:56:57.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過心情差到全日唔睇電話 自己自閉<br />\n或者一俾屋企人講兩句就好易躁同會惡意相向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都覺得啲性格垃圾到冇朋友"},{"pid":"df2edd356fb1da16e301d492bd6a98763ecf3a74","tid":299043,"uid":18456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:48:26.000Z","msg":"改"},{"pid":"3ce6f9b1fa474ba3743103efe010b8c1433ff2f9","tid":299043,"uid":120837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:31:03.000Z","msg":"我係好急個種人，見到d人慢、阻住個進度就會燥<br />\n例如：老母拖住細佬霸晒成條路慢慢行、搭lift唔㩒閂門、atm前面條友搞好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天氣熱情況會更嚴重<br />\n我都覺得自己脾氣臭到仆街，好易就燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc55498a24d7ea7624bf952662ee4870b230c98","tid":299043,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係office 長期閪面個d就真係乞人憎喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793b0ebf37bef566bdf9744cc649cfbd8be58251","tid":299043,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:47:35.000Z","msg":"依啲叫幼稚 ?    傻撚左呀 ?"},{"pid":"e1df18428916da3b611471fb0c9813eb1d49363b","tid":299043,"uid":82257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:52:27.000Z","msg":"乜呢啲唔係叫燥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}